data.description: Like a Model Home Inside & Out this Gorgeous 2 Story Brick 4 Bedroom Home with Study located in Timberbrook in Justin just North of Fort Worth features a Desirable Floor plan with Top of the Line upgrades & designer Finishes throughout. Built in 2021 by Sandlin Homes its just like new and ready for you! Why wait to build when you can move in NOW & have it ALL! Lovely Elevation with a 3 Car Garage, Gourmet Kitchen with Spacious Island, Stainless Steel Appliances & Rich White Quartz Countertops. The primary bedroom has a sitting area & the bathroom is oversized with a freestanding tub. Secondary Bedrooms share a Gameroom & Media Room upstairs Plus there is a junior suite with its own private bath which is ideal for next gen living. This community features a large & small Dog Park, Community Pool, Playground, Park & Walking trails.Awesome Location in a growing area with tons of New Shopping & Restaurants. Only 25 Minutes to downtown Fort Worth with quick commutes to Alliance & DFW Airport
